nodes.text: Tom Kenny (born July 13, 1962) is an American actor, voice actor, singer, and stand-up comedian who provided the voice of Biggs Darklighter in Star Wars: Rogue Squadron II: Rogue Leader and Star Wars: Rogue Squadron III: Rebel Strike and Nute Gunray, Nahdar Vebb, Tan Divo, Greedo, and the Rodian Silood in Star Wars: The Clone Wars TV series. He has also done numerous other voice roles, most notably the title character of SpongeBob SquarePants.
